metadata.name: I Survived - Gas Crisis
metadata.description:
To all of you with battle wounds from the CeFi crisis of 2022, let us take our shelter in memes. 

We're all hurting, some more than others ... but we stand together. 

The CeFi Survivors series is a way to commiserate with your fellow warriors. Wounded in battle as you may be, memes never die. 

Claim yours so you can always remember lessons learned. 

CeFi failed. DeFi didn't. Onwards.
